-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-26/barthle-says-european-tools-enough-to-halt-crisis-boersen-says.html
Norbert Barthle, parliamentary
budget spokesman for German Chancellor  Angela Merkel ’s  Christian
Democratic Union , said he is confident that the European Union’s
rescue programs will be sufficient to stabilize the euro zone,
 Boersen-Zeitung  newspaper reported today, citing an interview.  To contact the reporter on this story:
